---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
const title = "Powder Coating for Aluminium Window Frames – UAE Solutions";
const body = "<main class=\"container my-5\"><!-- Introduction --><section class=\"mb-5\"><h2>Introduction</h2><p>Aluminium window frames are a popular choice in Dubai for their sleek design and durability. However, constant exposure to intense sunlight, humidity, and airborne sand demands a robust surface treatment. That’s where <strong>powder coating</strong> comes in — providing a long-lasting, protective finish that enhances both appearance and performance.</p></section><!-- Benefits --><section class=\"mb-5\"><h2>Why Powder Coating for Aluminium Window Frames?</h2><ul><li>✅ <strong>UV resistance</strong> – prevents fading and chalking in Dubai’s sun</li><li>✅ <strong>Corrosion protection</strong> – resists rust in coastal or humid areas</li><li>✅ <strong>Scratch &amp; impact resistance</strong> – ideal for high-traffic buildings</li><li>✅ <strong>Aesthetic flexibility</strong> – available in 200+ RAL colors and textures</li><li>✅ <strong>Eco-friendly process</strong> – solvent-free and recyclable overspray</li></ul></section><!-- Process --><section class=\"mb-5\"><h2>Our 6-Stage Coating Process</h2><ol><li><strong>Degreasing &amp; Pre-treatment</strong> – Aluminium profiles are cleaned of oils and oxides for proper adhesion.</li><li><strong>Drying Oven</strong> – Moisture is removed in a controlled oven to prepare for coating.</li><li><strong>Electrostatic Powder Spraying</strong> – Powder is applied using precision equipment for even distribution.</li><li><strong>Curing in Oven (180–200°C)</strong> – The powder melts and chemically bonds to the surface.</li><li><strong>Cooling &amp; Inspection</strong> – Profiles are cooled and inspected for thickness, adhesion, and uniformity.</li><li><strong>Packaging &amp; Delivery</strong> – Carefully packed to prevent post-process damage.</li></ol></section><!-- Applications --><section class=\"mb-5\"><h2>Applications We Specialize In</h2><ul><li>Sliding &amp; folding window frames</li><li>Curtain wall systems</li><li>Villa and tower windows</li><li>Office and retail facades</li><li>High-rise residential developments</li></ul></section><!-- Why Choose Us --><section class=\"mb-5\"><h2>Why Choose Us in Dubai?</h2><ul><li>✅ Local facility with <strong>quick turnaround</strong></li><li>✅ <strong>Batch and custom job</strong> support</li><li>✅ ISO-certified &amp; Qualicoat-compliant</li><li>✅ Collection and delivery across the UAE</li><li>✅ Color-matching to existing profiles available</li></ul></section><!-- Gallery / Case Study --><section class=\"mb-5\"><h2>Case Study: Coastal Villa in Jumeirah</h2><blockquote class=\"blockquote\"><p>“The old anodized frames were heavily faded. After powder coating in RAL 7016 anthracite, the transformation was incredible — both in look and lifespan.”</p><footer class=\"blockquote-footer\"><p>Client from Jumeirah</p></footer></blockquote><p><em>[Insert before/after image here]</em></p></section><!-- FAQ --><section class=\"mb-5\"><h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class=\"accordion\" id=\"faqAccordion\"><div class=\"accordion-item\"><h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"faq1\"><button class=\"accordion-button\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#collapse1\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"collapse1\">\r\n                                                      Can you match existing frame colors?\r\n                                                    </button></h2><div class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\" id=\"collapse1\" aria-labelledby=\"faq1\" data-bs-parent=\"#faqAccordion\"><div class=\"accordion-body\">Yes, we offer custom color-matching and stock over 200 RAL shades.</div></div></div><div class=\"accordion-item\"><h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"faq2\"><button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#collapse2\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse2\">\r\n                                                      How long does the coating last?\r\n                                                    </button></h2><div class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" id=\"collapse2\" aria-labelledby=\"faq2\" data-bs-parent=\"#faqAccordion\"><div class=\"accordion-body\">Typically 15–25 years with proper maintenance, even in harsh environments.</div></div></div><div class=\"accordion-item\"><h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"faq3\"><button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#collapse3\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse3\">\r\n                                                      Do you coat assembled frames or just profiles?\r\n                                                    </button></h2><div class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" id=\"collapse3\" aria-labelledby=\"faq3\" data-bs-parent=\"#faqAccordion\"><div class=\"accordion-body\">We specialize in coating <strong>disassembled aluminium profiles</strong> for best results.</div></div></div></div></section><!-- Contact CTA --><section class=\"text-center mb-5\"><h2>Request a Quote Today</h2><p>Looking to powder coat your aluminium window frames in Dubai? Contact us now for a free consultation and lead time estimate.</p><p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/contact\">Contact Us</a> <a class=\"btn btn-success ms-2\" href=\"https://wa.me/971559680609\">WhatsApp Us</a></p></section></main><footer class=\"bg-light text-center py-4\"><p><small>Serving clients in Dubai, Sharjah, Ajman, and across the UAE. All powder coating work complies with Qualicoat and ISO standards.</small></p></footer>";
